<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ900724-0093</DOCNO><DOCID>900724-0093.</DOCID><HL>   Loral Wins Air Force Contract</HL><DATE>07/24/90</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B5</SO><CO>   LOR MD</CO><GV>DEFENSE DEPARTMENT (DEF)</GV><LP>   WASHINGTON -- Loral Corp. was given a $71.5 million AirForce contract for development and operation of aircrew-training systems for MC-130 aircraft.                                                                                                       </LP><TEXT>   McDonnell Douglas Missile Systems Co., a unit of McDonnellDouglas Corp., was issued an $18.5 million combined contractfor engineering of the Tomahawk weapon system.</TEXT></DOC>